HEADWORD: Was
<hw>Was</hw> <pr>(w⟦ocr⟧z)</pr>. <ety>[AS. <ets>w⟦ae⟧s</ets>, 2d pers.
<ets>w⟦aemac⟧re</ets>, 3d pers. <ets>w⟦ae⟧s</ets>, pl.
